==Dutch==

===Proper noun===
'''Miep'''

# A female [[given name]]. Short form the name [[Maria]], the [[Dutch]] equivalent of [[Mary]].

[[Category:Female given names]]

===Dutch female [[hypokoristic]] forming===

In Dutch a typical [[hypokoristic]] pet form forming is to trunk the whole name and add a -P- or a -S- to it. Miep is such an example.

